    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride at a reasonable price? This vehicle is a great everyday driver that gets the job done! It shows some expected wear and tear both inside and out \u2014 you'll notice some cosmetic imperfections on the exterior and the interior reflects its years of use \u2014 but mechanically it's running and ready to go. If you're after a practical, budget-conscious option that doesn't break the bank, this could be the right fit for you!",
      "price": 16000.0,
