      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for a solid, dependable ride without breaking the bank? This vehicle is a great option for everyday driving \u2014 it runs and gets you where you need to go! You'll notice some cosmetic wear inside and out, as expected for a car of its age and mileage, but it's been kept in functional condition. A few minor imperfections here and there, but nothing that takes away from its practicality. Priced fairly to reflect its true condition \u2014 come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives, but buyers should go in with realistic expectations. The exterior shows noticeable wear including visible scratches, scuffs, and minor dents that are consistent with a vehicle that has seen regular use over the years. The interior is functional but shows signs of age \u2014 expect worn upholstery, some fading, and general wear on high-contact surfaces. Mechanically, the car gets you where you need to go, though we recommend a pre-purchase inspection as there may be deferred maintenance items or minor issues that a new owner will want to address. This is a solid choice for a budget-conscious buyer who needs reliable transportation and doesn't mind putting a little work in.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Solid & Dependable \u2014 A Practical Choice for Smart Shoppers! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 it runs reliably and is ready to handle your daily driving needs! You'll notice some cosmetic wear on the exterior and interior that comes with its age and use, and there may be a minor mechanical item or two worth addressing down the road. But the fundamentals are sound \u2014 this is an honest, no-nonsense car that gets you where you need to go! A great opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer who wants dependable transportation without the premium price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself! \ud83d\ude4c",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in poor condition, and we are committed to full transparency so buyers can make an informed decision. The exterior shows significant wear, including multiple dents, deep scratches, and areas of paint fading or chipping. There is visible rust in several spots on the body panels. The interior is worn with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard trim, and general grime throughout the cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 expect to invest in repairs before relying on it for regular use. Brakes, suspension, and other wear items should be inspected by a qualified mechanic prior to purchase. This car is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation on a tight budget and understands the trade-offs involved. No major hidden surprises \u2014 what you see is what you get.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered at $46,500, and that price is a true reflection of its outstanding, mint condition \u2014 this car is as close to perfect as a used vehicle can be. The exterior is immaculate: the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Every panel is straight and true, the trim is pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without any chips or cracks. The interior matches the exterior in every way \u2014 the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show virtually no wear, and everything smells fresh and clean. All electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended with no issues whatsoever. Under the hood, the engine is clean and dry, with no leaks, no unusual noises, and strong, smooth performance. The drivetrain is equally impressive \u2014 shifts are crisp, braking is confident, and the ride is solid and rattle-free. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a used vehicle that genuinely looks and drives like new. Buyers who demand the very best will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    }
